techmeme.title: Humanoid robot startup Figure raised a $1B+ Series C led by Parkway Venture Capital at a post-money valuation of $39B, up from $2.6B in February 2024 (Jackie Davalos/Bloomberg)
HR software provider Workday agrees to acquire Sana, an AI startup specializing in workplace tools, for $1.1B; the transaction is set to close in Workday's Q4 (Nicholas G. Miller/Wall Street Journal)
Israel-based Vega, which offers an AI-based security analytics platform, raised $65M in seed and Series A led by Accel at a $400M valuation (Meytal Vaizberg/Globes)
Google launches the Agent Payments Protocol, or AP2, designed to securely facilitate agent-led payments across platforms, with the support of over 60 companies (Sabrina Ortiz/ZDNET)
OpenAI says it is developing a "different ChatGPT experience" for teens and plans to use age-prediction tech to bar kids under 18 from the standard version (Megan Morrone/Axios)
